        "chunk_summaries": [
            "The group spent the segment introducing themselves and their research areas, which span computational biophysics, chemical biology, and nanoparticle research. Cathy Murphy facilitated the introductions and established the meeting structure by assigning a scribe (Seth Childers) and a reporter (Abhishek Singharoy). The group ended the chunk in a procedural state, ready to begin discussing the core challenge of signaling at different scales.",
